<plot>Zak, a smart, funny and all-around nice guy is still coming to terms with his ex-girlfriend's recent passing. Determined to get on with his life, Zak agrees to go on a blind date with the cute and quirky girl named Olivia. The date comes to an abrupt end when Zak's dead ex shows up with an ultimatum. Some relationships never die.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?087365</url></doc>
